{"tid":1593404,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"續拒港交所提購！倫交所：上海才是中國金融中心","createTime":"2019-09-25T05:10:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T06:31:04.000Z","uid":133680,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e4f9cdf6312e136dd6880b52986730e09e569d87","tid":1593404,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:10:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190924/mobile/bkn-20190924211053259-0924_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190924%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190924211053259-0924_00842_001.html&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9AwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=7bbff656\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190924/mobile/bkn-20190924211053259-0924_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外國傳媒報道，倫敦證券交易所行政總裁David Schwimmer周二(24日)稱，香港未來可能無法處於「具有競爭力的地位」，並認為上海才是中國的金融中心。此言正值香港交易所(00388)尋求收購倫交所之際，反映後者依然不願意接受港交所早前提出的併購計劃。<br />\n港交所行政總裁李小加則指出，鑑於中國銀行體系中，有27萬億美元資金需要配置，現在正是打造一家全球交易所的時候。<br />\n兩人在中國放寬資本管制的可能性上亦存在分歧，Schwimmer稱，這是「不可避免的」，李小加則認為，需要20年或更長時間。<br />\n對於倫交所拒絕港交所收購的其中一個關注點是港交所的管治結構，即港府持有港交所約6%股權，在13名董事中共有6名是港府委任。<br />\n李小加指出，「如果交易可以進行的話，我們對改變管治結構持開放態度。」"},{"pid":"c979f8cae1897419892382870ecaf396f14dadc4","tid":1593404,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:11:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"22424840cbb86da615101f0d211ca4343c34fcc0","tid":1593404,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:15:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5745e262d6ded20fd8383fd361dd3f01b063a4f2","tid":1593404,"uid":133680,"